{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/extras/Ab1.png?t=1738068932\" />.<br><br>Art of Blades is a hand-drawn top-down isometric simple hack-and-slash.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/extras/RDgif.gif?t=1738068932\" /><br><br>The art is inspired by Japanese manga and anime.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/extras/Ab3.png?t=1738068932\" /><br><br> The gameplay is a very simple hack-and-slash based on rock paper scissors. Scissors to attack, rock to block, and paper to dodge. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/extras/F34BDA4A-668E-4790-90DE-8FC88FE7D8D2.png?t=1738068932\" /><br><br>Depending on what enemy is in front of you you choose the proper action to deal with it. <br><br>Art of Blades is set in a futuristic fantasy feudal Japan-inspired country in a world with robots and magic (naruto inspired but more sci-fi). <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/extras/Ab2.png?t=1738068932\" /><br><br>You play as the Wanderer, someone who is traveling around the world looking for \u201cinspiration\u201d, then one day he unexpectedly encounters an S.O.S drone which starts him on this journey in Art of Blades.<br><br>*Art of Blades is an original intellectual property of SamuereRS.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738068932","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/page.bg.jpg?t=1738068932","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2883740/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738068932","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store